<p><cs><col><b>Cestuy que trust</b></col> <pr>(<?/)</pr> <ety>[norm.
F.]</ety>, <cd>a person who has the equitable and beneficial interest in
property, the legal interest in which is vested in a trustee.</cd>
<au>Wharton.</au> -- <col><b>Cestuy que use</b></col> <pr>(<?/)</pr>
<ety>[Norm. F.]</ety>, <cd>a person for whose use land, etc., is granted
to another.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Cesura</ent>⟦br⟧
